            Our commitment to quality, precision, and customer satisfaction has made us a trusted 
            name in the industry. From small-scale custom projects to large industrial contracts, 
            we approach every job with the same dedication to excellence.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
